headline.main: Soccer: Ibrahimovic, Mings Charged With Violent Conduct
headline.print_headline: Soccer: Ibrahimovic, Mings Charged With Violent Conduct

lead_paragraph: Manchester United's Zlatan Ibrahimovic and Bournemouth defender Tyrone Mings were charged with violent conduct by the Football Association on Monday.
